    Use explicit visibility
    Use explicit visibility instead of the default package private level.

<p>Use explicit visibility for attributes instead of the
default package private level.  For example, change</p>

<pre>
public class Foo {
  int myInt;
  ...
}
</pre>

<p>to</p>

<pre>
public class Foo {
  private int myInt;
  ...
}
</pre>
